This directory contains the user-facing HTML manuals for the Regalia app
(Chinese and English versions). Each manual is a self-contained HTML file
with embedded CSS and JavaScript (no external resources).

License classification by file:
  - Regalia-v1.1.0-manual-zh.html: AGPL v3 (original Regalia work)
      Chinese user manual for Regalia v1.1.0 (current).
      Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
  - Regalia-v1.1.0-manual-en.html: AGPL v3 (original Regalia work)
      English user manual for Regalia v1.1.0 (current).
      Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.

The manuals are AGPL v3 because they are original documentation created by
the Regalia project, not derived from any third-party GPL work. The embedded
diagrams, wireframes, and changelog text are all original.

v1.1.0 (2026.7.5) Phase 58 changes:
  - Regalia-v1.1.0-manual-{zh,en}.html: Phase 58 changelog entry. Phase 58
    documents: (1) every-5-moves PGN {} eval annotation — at moves 5, 10, 15,
    20, ..., the PGN {} comment now includes a human-readable eval-bar-mirroring
    fragment, auto-localized via T() reading the global _lang variable. Format:
    "均势 (-0.10) D22 SD34 (1%W/96%D/3%L)" (Chinese) /
    "Equal (-0.10) D22 SD34 (1%W/96%D/3%L)" (English). White-perspective.
    (2) stopLatch TOCTOU race fix in StockfishNative.java — bestmove handler
    now atomically captures-and-clears _stopLatch under _stopLatchLock;
    timeout path only arms discard flag if it still owns the latch. (3) Heartbeat
    deadlock fix in StockfishNative.java — dedicated _writerLock decoupled from
    `this` monitor so shutdown's join is not blocked by heartbeat's writer I/O.

v1.1.0 (2026.7.5) Phase 57+ changes:
  - Regalia-v1.1.0-manual-{zh,en}.html: Current version. Phase 57+ changelog
    entry at the top of Appendix A (newest-first order). Phase 57+ documents
    code-review-driven preventive hardening: (1) pgn-standard.js single-line
    PGN tag-stripping regex fix (preventive — parser not on main code path),
    (2) chess960.js isChess960CastlingLegal king-position lookup uses s.wk/s.bk
    cache (with board-scan fallback), (3) ai-bridge.js WDL percentage display
    divide-by-zero guard, (4) StockfishNative.java postJsCallback activity-
    lifecycle guard (isFinishing/isDestroyed check before evaluateJavascript —
    prevents HyperOS 3 IllegalStateException crash during engine-init retries),
    (5) EngineService.java wake-lock bounded 30-minute timeout (prevents
    indefinite CPU wake if OEM silently kills service), (6) res/README.license
    LIC-2 stale version reference (v1.0.8 → v1.1.0). Also adds pure-English
    UBIQUITOUS_LANGUAGE.md at the project root — 80+ domain terminology
    reference for developer/domain-expert conversations.

v1.1.0 (2026.7.4) changes:
  - Regalia-v1.1.0-manual-{zh,en}.html: Phase 57 changelog entry. Phase 57
    documents:
    (1) portrait review mode move-list scroll positioning fix — the Phase 56
    manual-scrollTop calculation used offsetTop (which is relative to
    .review-overlay, the offsetParent, NOT relative to .review-moves); in
    portrait this included the board's full height (256-320px), causing the
    active move to be clamped to scrollHeight-clientHeight (scrolled to
    bottom) and not centered. Replaced with getBoundingClientRect-based
    calculation that computes the active move's position relative to
    .review-moves, regardless of orientation/layout/offsetParent chain.
    (2) visual-annotation cache residue fix — _computeInitialPositionAnnotations
    now reads reviewStates[0].state (the actual initial position) instead of
    gameState (the LIVE mid-game state); enterReview now clears the '_initial'
    cache key at entry to prevent stale annotations from a previous review
    session persisting at step 0. Chess960-compatible (reviewStates[0].state
    carries the Chess960 starting position with spid).
  - Phase 56 (previous): landscape review nav-button scroll-to-top fix,
    PGN timeout annotation ([Termination "Time forfeit"] + {<color> wins by
    timeout}), first-move timing sync (_turnStartTime + gameClocks reset in
    _resetGameUIState), UCI command ordering refinement for Chess960 +
    TimeControl.
  - Phase 53 (older): green-arrow check-response, red-arrow discovered-
    check fix, king-position staleness fix, FEN-import/exitSetup state-
    pollution fix, portrait/landscape review layout unification, stats
    visual-annotation cutoff, king-control-arrow legality filter, nav-button
    center-align.

v1.0.9 (2026.7.2) and earlier:
  - Old version manuals (v1.0.4–v1.0.9) have been deleted; only the current
    v1.1.0 manual is distributed. The v1.1.0 manual's Appendix A contains
    the complete historical changelog (Phase 52 and earlier) for reference.
